Post 20761 has Killfest's history and stuff.

::Killfest::

A pod enters the atmosphere of earth, flying at the ground at an 
alarming rate. It slows down at the last second, touching down in what 
would be known as australia in the future.

The pod, damaged but not designed to let its occupant out since it was 
a prison pod, releases its hold on Killfest's mind, the terrorist 
slowly waking
